OL,3,CDairy farmer with huge hernia waits
OL,4,Cfive years for surgery
OL,6,FGranada Report journalist has followed
OL,7,FWinston's story
OL,9,FA former dairy farmer from Crewe, who
OL,10,Fhas been waiting for an NHS operation
OL,11,Ffor almost five years says he has
OL,12,Fnearly given up hope.
OL,14,FWinston Baldwin, 75, has been living
OL,15,Fwith a triple hernia since 2019 which
OL,16,Fhas grown so large he can now barely
OL,17,Fwalk and has moved to a care home.
OL,19,FHis story has been featured on ITV
OL,20,FGranada Reports four times, ever since
OL,21,Fhis treatment was delayed .
