OL,3,CDairy farmer with huge hernia waits
OL,4,Cfive years for surgery
OL,6,FIn 2022, Winston was told his hernia
OL,7,Fwas too large to be operated on, but
OL,8,Fthere was a glimmer of hope in March
OL,9,F2023 when two surgeons from Arrowe
OL,10,FPark hospital on the Wirral got in
OL,11,Ftouch to
OL,13,FAlmost a year on though, Winston is
OL,14,Fstill waiting, despite having a number
OL,15,Fof pre-operation appointments.
OL,17,FHe told ITV Granada Reports' Mel
OL,18,FBarham: "I don't have a life. I am
OL,19,Fmore or less trapped in my room.
