OL,3,CDairy farmer with huge hernia waits
OL,4,Cfive years for surgery
OL,6,F"It's like carrying a bag of potatoes
OL,7,Fin front of you but it's there all the
OL,8,Ftime. You can't put it down, put it
OL,9,Fback again, it's always with you."
OL,11,FWinston's condition, which is when
OL,12,Finternal organs escape through a
OL,13,Fweakness in the muscle, had grown even
OL,14,Fmore since Granada Reports last filmed
OL,15,Fwith him in November 2023.
OL,17,FWinston said: "I had Covid about a
OL,18,Fmonth ago and it has made the hernia
OL,19,Fgrow, so it is actually huge now.
