OL,3,CDairy farmer with huge hernia waits
OL,4,Cfive years for surgery
OL,6,F"It's made it more difficult for me to
OL,7,Fbreathe and walk, and I certainly
OL,8,Fdon't want you to see it."
OL,10,FWinston has received a number of pre-
OL,11,Fop appointments but is still yet to be
OL,12,Fgiven a date for the operation.
OL,14,FHe is due to have another pre-op on
OL,15,FFriday 23 February, which has been
OL,16,Fbrought forward from April.
OL,18,FHe said although he has nothing but
OL,19,Fgratitude for his surgeons he is
OL,20,Fbeyond frustrated at the system that
OL,21,Fhas kept him waiting.
